doing so I did not change the meaning. Words and comments in brackets are
mine alone and are errors my responsibility.
The bottom line here is that ECLS might be useful in treating a variety of
pulmonary infections. Certainly more data are need, but this report is a
hopeful indication. - Mod.CHC
